00:01:03.780 --> 00:01:07.540
the mikes for our YouTube audience.
Without any further ado, please join me in

00:01:07.540 --> 00:01:08.850
welcoming Brad.
Thank you very much.

00:01:08.850 --> 00:01:17.490
BRAD MATSEN: Hi everybody.
Like the rest of the world, I live with Google

